name.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Star2Star Contact Center Click to Dial

short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: This Chrome extension detects phone numbers on web pages and enables click to dial via Star2Star Contact Center Agent Panel.

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
You must have Star2Star Service Insight or Contact Center service in order to use this browser extension.

User Guide available at https://knowledge.star2star.com/kb/2964

Terms of Use available at http://www.star2star.com/applications-terms-of-use
